; Coverage for draft.cc: year directive does not affect xact date (#707)
year 2023

2024/06/15 Grocery Store
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test --now 2026/07/01 xact "06/15" "Grocery"
2026/06/15 Grocery Store
    Expenses:Food                             $10.00
    Assets:Cash
end test
